  // Leadership (Co-President / People Lead). Top people-strategy role: owns
  // Action Items delegation, reviews, and the People Dashboard. Reports to the
  // Board (represented here by SUPER_ADMIN). Added in the People Strategy layer.
  // (Formerly named CPO; renamed to LEADERSHIP in the Phase 5 cleanup.)
  LEADERSHIP
  // DEPRECATED legacy alias for LEADERSHIP. Kept in the enum so that any client
  // generated from this schema can still DESERIALIZE the old value, and so a
  // deployment that runs against a database where the value was not yet renamed
  // does not 500. Application code normalizes CPO -> LEADERSHIP (see
  // lib/admin-subtypes.ts). Do NOT write this value. Remove only in a future
  // "contract" migration once every deployment + row is on LEADERSHIP.
